  "texts": [
    "Hence, early detection plays a pivotal role in combating disinformation as it can help prevent its widespread dissemination.",
    "However, in order to effectively detect disinformation, most of existing approaches require a certain time lapse after the spread of each content.",
    "Currently, the majority of existing approaches are primarily monolingual and predominantly focused on the English language.",
    "Regrettably, many other popular and regional languages have not yet been adequately considered in these approaches.",
    "Multilingual analysis of disinformation offers a more comprehensive understanding of the phenomenon, enabling the identification of non-varying features that transcend language boundaries."
  ],
